{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e591-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"152"},"text":"§ 152.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Competitive procedures","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In division C, the term “competitive procedures” means procedures under which an executive agency enters into a contract pursuant to full and open competition. The term also includes—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e592-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" procurement of architectural or engineering services conducted in accordance with chapter 11 of title 40;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e593-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the competitive selection of basic research proposals resulting from a general solicitation and the peer review or scientific review (as appropriate) of those proposals;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e594-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" the procedures established by the Administrator of General Services for the multiple awards schedule program of the General Services Administration if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e595-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" participation in the program has been open to all responsible sources; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e596-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" orders and contracts under those procedures result in the lowest overall cost alternative to meet the needs of the Federal Government;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e597-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" procurements conducted in furtherance of section 15 of the Small Business Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s644"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 644","children":[],"tail":") as long as all responsible business concerns that are entitled to submit offers for those procurements are permitted to compete; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e598-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2","identifier":"/us/usc/t41/s152/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a competitive selection of research proposals resulting from a general solicitation and peer review or scientific review (as appropriate) solicited pursuant to section 9 of that Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s638"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 638","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id83b5e599-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/350/s3"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–350, §